# GNAIAAAC Partner Onboarding Portal

## Welcome
This portal guides your organization through the deployment of the GNAIAAAC AI Learning Ecosystem.

---

## Step 1 — Sign Licensing Agreement
Organizations purchase the license.
Organizations obtain their own accreditation.

---

## Step 2 — Access Documentation
Download:
- AI Learning Path
- Sleeping Agent Framework
- Deployment Blueprint
- Governance Charter
- Curriculum Map
- Teacher Certification Program

---

## Step 3 — Training
Your team receives:
- AI literacy training
- workflow training
- Sleeping Agent safety training
- teacher certification modules

---

## Step 4 — Deployment
Choose your deployment model:
- Individual learners
- Classrooms
- Community hubs
- National programs

---

## Step 5 — Monitoring & Evaluation
Use dashboards to track:
- learning progress
- system usage
- safety logs
- community impact

---

## Support
Email + documentation + optional premium support.

